{"tid":1186310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲人點解咁重奴性 源自教育制","createTime":"2019-06-04T23:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T01:35:31.000Z","uid":121911,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b235533bbac61773be4ba47a204abfb37208ac5a","tid":1186310,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T23:57:29.000Z","msg":"望一望亞洲 邊到奴性重既國家既教育唔係注重考試？<br />\n<br />\n咁當然歐美國家都睇考試，但同時佢地都會著重你係咪真係學緊野而唔係一味塞比你就算。<br />\n<br />\n睇返中國 同 香港 一個公開考試操到學生人唔似人 一鋪定生死咁，導致出到黎做野會覺得做錯dddd野 / 唔聽老細話，就會失敗咁。以工程行業為例 上司塞完個project就一句叫你搞點佢就算 <br />\n<br />\n寒窗苦讀十幾年 咩反抗力都磨到無晒 覺得捱落去會有轉機有成果 但工作=/=讀書 你做到狗咁 老細只會覺得你好用 繼續比野你做 唔會同你客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ceeac5ae4708790766cd551334d000bf06d4d7","tid":1186310,"uid":120123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T00:12:58.000Z","msg":"我一向覺得華人社會就係一個容錯性好低的社會。<br />\n就算例如你take gap year d HR都會問長問短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c351cb9959719c9357cfd86bf423a63bcc8eed","tid":1186310,"uid":254371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c1ceeac5ae4708790766cd551334d000bf06d4d7","tid":1186310,"uid":120123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T00:12:58.000Z","msg":"我一向覺得華人社會就係一個容錯性好低的社會。<br />\n就算例如你take gap year d HR都會問長問短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T00:15:39.000Z","msg":"鬼仔鬼妹abc take a gap year=生活態度<br />\n香港人=廢人"},{"pid":"9540377dba9d9d515b1383729fa30d4d91dd2859","tid":1186310,"uid":120123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"42c351cb9959719c9357cfd86bf423a63bcc8eed","tid":1186310,"uid":254371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c1ceeac5ae4708790766cd551334d000bf06d4d7","tid":1186310,"uid":120123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"re